Syntax x = x (p)
  Where p Isa object
    Else "You can only 'x' objects."

Add To Every object
  Verb x
    Does
      "You 'x' the" Say p. "$$.$n"
      "You 'x' the $1."
  End Verb x.
End Add.

The o Isa object At l
  Name shiny sharp long thing
End The o.

The l Isa location
  Exit w,e,s,n To l.
End The l.

Start At l.